{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"9130f590-3acb-4874-bc64-efa606500bd8","content":"Good news — in .NET 10, `dotnet test` uses Microsoft.Testing.Platform **by default**. The `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property is no longer needed and can be removed.\n\nYou still need `EnableMSTestRunner` — that tells MSTest to build as an MTP executable. The change is only that `dotnet test` now natively speaks the MTP protocol without the opt-in flag.","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01U3hEKs42U6BGnYrSiuUxdK","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Removing redundant property"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_012kHBvnT22ZVs29yJ6hsMHN","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-47b5bb31818147f99e251baf2efd6f4a/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-47b5bb31818147f99e251baf2efd6f4a/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"e30e7800-0e65-4e21-a33b-c22e12811f67","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is on .NET 10 SDK (10.0.100) and is using MSTest with Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP) via `EnableMSTestRunner`. They have `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` set to `true`.\n\nIn .NET 10, `dotnet test` natively uses Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP) as the default test runner. The `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property was needed in .NET 9 to opt into MTP support with `dotnet test`, but in .NET 10 it's no longer necessary — MTP is the default.\n\n\nSince `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` is now redundant on .NET 10, the user can remove it. However, `EnableMSTestRunner` still needs to stay — it's what configures the MSTest project to actually use the MTP runner and build as an executable, which is separate from whether `dotnet test` knows how to communicate with MTP.","outputTokens":579,"requestId":"4C16:3F94EE:DC1D36:110B6E6:6A012A94"},"id":"24915598-be1d-4cad-b5d1-44c54da3adbb","timestamp":"2026-05-11T01:02:21.788Z","parentId":"413fb276-ad7d-4cb4-9f16-f2e662d5ad91"}
